<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الضُّحَى<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٢:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَالضُّحَى <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَاللَّيْلِ إِذَا سَجَى <span class="c2">(٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[الضحى: ١، ٢]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{إِذَا سَجَى}</span>: <span class="c2">«اسْتَوَى»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{سَجَى}</span>: <span class="c2">«أَظْلَمَ وَسَكَنَ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>